Watch and learn how to tightline your eyes with these tips from Celebrity Makeup Artist @misha212. 

Step 1: Start by lining your lash line and upper waterline with MicroLiner Ink in Black. 

Step 2: Use the YANE HAKE Precision Eye Brush to extend the liner outward, creating a wing.

Step 3: For added depth, trace the lash line with ArchLiner Ink. 

Step 4: Add drama with Kajal InkArtist in Nippon Noir, applied along the lower waterline. 

Step 5: Finish the look with a few swipes of ImperialLash MascaraInk. 

#ShiseidoMakeup #JapaneseBeauty
